{
  "_comment": [
    "iTerm2 Dynamic Profile for screencast recordings - Default-colours variant.",
    "Lives inside the iterm_for_recordly/ folder alongside its AppleScript.",
    "Symlinked into ~/Library/Application Support/iTerm2/DynamicProfiles/ so iTerm2 auto-loads it.",
    "Edit this file at its real location, not via the symlink.",
    "",
    "This profile mirrors the recording-friendly tweaks of the 'Recording' profile",
    "(Menlo Bold 16, non-blinking box cursor, bells silenced, no thin strokes),",
    "but uses the 'Dark Background' colour scheme - i.e. the colours currently",
    "applied to the user's main iTerm2 'Default' profile (GUID A2D5D943-5D58-4D54-926C-15FA512FC301).",
    "Snapshot taken from the plist at 2026-04-16.",
    "",
    "If you change colours in your main Default profile and want this recording",
    "variant to track them, re-extract with plistlib and replace the colour blocks below.",
    "",
    "Launched via iterm_for_recordly.applescript --default"
  ],
